      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPARKLE CORNER (3) has been narrowly beaten in his past couple over 1400m and drops back to 1207m here today. He can find the front form the draw and Ramoly has a good record aboard the gelding. Rates highly on his recent form and if he can run up to those figures, he'll be hard to reel in. DEEP DISCRETION (7) bolted in at her latest attempt at this track and trip three starts ago and has been solid in defeat in two runs since. Back to the scene of the crime today where she's never missed the placings. Likely to be back in the run but as she showed three back, she can round her rivals up with ease. LUCKEE FLORAN (5) led and won over 1100m last time out and steps up to 1200m once again. Can sit on the speed from the inside alley and won't be far away. GOLD KEEPER (1) is right on the cusp and can go one better in this easier race today. ENTICING (9) is third-up now and can improve getting out in trip.",
